reviewText: This is great content but a terrible way to convey this content.  It is completely automated and most of the projects submitted where plagiarized.   This course should be done in person or via live-stream.  They required you to produce documents for your project without providing you a template and in some cases without explaining what they are.  There are other better ways to take this class
This is not a 100% online study
The final assignment was pretty good and the peer review process helped me to understand the various documents.  The quizzes involve simple regurgitation and are pretty useless.
Every one should do this and learn something
good, i learnt alot in very short time. I hope others also learn as quick

The Define phase lays the foundation of the project and it is very important to get all the elements & nuances right from the begining. This course has exactly emphasised on these aspects of the project and helps lay a strong and lean foundation towards a successful project.
very useful and has many tools which will help me to upgrade my skills
